#Business101 in 3 short mins with @thealbertpreciado
-
How to turn your idea(s) into reality.. Series A, B and C.. the tangible and intangible value when creating a brand and launching products, choosing when to raise capital and who to bring on as a partner and WHEN (good money vs bad money), allocating funds appropriately and managing/leveraging relationships which can take you and your brand(s) far beyond over a small injection of money
-
#Limitless #Driven #KnowledgeIsPower #EducationMatters

Small clip from an interview I did with my friend @thealbertpreciado this past weekend highlighting bits and pieces of when and how I got started in the crazy world of business.. most don’t know this yet but I was 11 years old when I started my first company in 1996
-
The 🔑 to being able to conquer my goals has been my ability to always stay in a positive state of mind & surround myself with like-minded loyal people! 😏🙌🏽👨🏽‍💻
-
#Limitless #Driven

Everybody go follow and connect with a friend of mine Jas @LIMITLESS and show your support as I challenge him to a 6-Week Beach Body Transformation on his 35th birthday!!! That’s right… NO CAKE!!! At one point, Jas weighed over 450 Lbs and is one of the most hard-working, dedicated and inspirational people I know. I’m challenging him and everyone else to #ReinventYourself because Health is Wealth
-
Take part in the movement and join the #LimitlessChallenge - email your before pictures to challenge@limitlessx.com for a chance to participate, and get ready to GRIND for that transformation with CASH PRIZES. In 6 Weeks, you can have a strong body and wallet filled with CASH. 😎 💰💸 — @limitless

.

node.text:
A strong mind, body and soul will overcome anything. Diet and regular physical activity is important to maintain a balance between work and life. A major benefit of physical activity is to increase those energy levels, self- esteem and attitude, which can help everything else in life become much easier. Whether it’s sports, lifting weights or running, build schedules and workout plans around your daily routine
.
This will build confidence in channeling your inner beast and recognize your limits. Psych yourself up to give you a mental edge because it is a great sensation in ending the day like a champion. You’ll be left wanting more. Train the beast, invest in yourself, strive to become the best version of YOU 💪🏽💪🏽💪🏽
.
#December2021 #BeastMode #UltimateBodyTransformation #WorkHard #TighteningUp
